main event: Several round objects were seen at a great height in the sky in Edmonton, Alberta, Canada on June 29, 1959.
interesting points: The objects were approximately the size of a basketball and were white in color.
The objects appeared and disappeared at irregular intervals.
The objects were seen to be moving in a horizontal direction at a very high speed.
No sound was audible during the observation.
The observation was made from the ground and lasted for 5 minutes.
sighted object: several round white objects in the sky
